STATE of Louisiana
v.
Terry Wayne PARRIS NO. 2019-KH-0385 Supreme Court of Louisiana. May 20, 2019

Denied. Applicant has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review and fails to show that any exception permits his successive filing. See State ex rel. Farris v. State, 15-0700 (La. 2/5/16), 183 So.3d 505 .
